msgid "List webhook endpoints"
msgstr "Daftar akhir webhook"

msgid "Get all configured webhook endpoints for this store."
msgstr "Dapatkan semua akhir titik webhook yang dikonfigurasi untuk toko ini."

msgid "Create webhook endpoint"
msgstr "Buat akhir webhook"

msgid ""
"Create a new webhook endpoint.\n"
"\n"
"        The secret will be auto-generated and returned in the response.\n"
"        **Store the secret securely** - it will only be shown once.\n"
"\n"
"        Example events: `order.created`, `order.shipped`, `payment.received`"
msgstr ""
"Buat akhir titik webhook baru.\n"
"\n"
"Rahasia akan dihasilkan secara otomatis dan dikembalikan dalam respons.\n"
"**Simpan rahasia secara aman** - hanya akan ditampilkan sekali.\n"
"\n"
"Contoh acara: `order.created`, `order.shipped`, `payment.received`"

msgid "Validation error"
msgstr "Kesalahan validasi"

msgid "Get webhook endpoint"
msgstr "Dapatkan akhir webhook"

msgid "Get details of a specific webhook endpoint."
msgstr "Dapatkan detail akhir titik webhook tertentu."

msgid "Endpoint not found"
msgstr "Akhir tidak ditemukan"

msgid "Update webhook endpoint"
msgstr "Perbarui akhir webhook"

msgid "Update an existing webhook endpoint."
msgstr "Perbarui akhir webhook yang sudah ada."

msgid "Delete webhook endpoint"
msgstr "Hapus akhir webhook"

msgid "Delete a webhook endpoint. All delivery logs will also be deleted."
msgstr "Hapus akhir titik webhook. Semua log pengiriman juga akan dihapus."

msgid "Endpoint deleted"
msgstr "Akhir telah dihapus"

msgid "Test webhook endpoint"
msgstr "Uji akhir webhook"

msgid ""
"Send a test webhook to verify the endpoint configuration.\n"
"\n"
"    This sends a `test.webhook` event with sample data to verify\n"
"    that the endpoint is reachable and properly configured."
msgstr ""
"Kirim webhook uji untuk memverifikasi konfigurasi akhir titik.\n"
"\n"
"Ini mengirimkan acara `test.webhook` dengan data contoh untuk memverifikasi\n"
"bahwa akhir titik dapat diakses dan dikonfigurasikan dengan benar."

msgid "Rotate webhook secret"
msgstr "Putar rahasia webhook"

msgid ""
"Generate a new secret for a webhook endpoint.\n"
"\n"
"    The new secret will be returned in the response. **Store it securely** "
"-\n"
"    it will not be shown again. You will need to update your webhook\n"
"    receiver to use the new secret."
msgstr ""
"Buat rahasia baru untuk akhir titik webhook.\n"
"\n"
"Rahasia baru akan dikembalikan dalam respons. **Simpan secara aman** -\n"
"rahasia tersebut tidak akan ditampilkan lagi. Anda perlu memperbarui "
"penerima webhook\n"
"Anda untuk menggunakan rahasia baru."

msgid "Reset endpoint failures"
msgstr "Atur ulang kegagalan akhir"

msgid ""
"Reset the failure count for a webhook endpoint.\n"
"\n"
"    This re-enables an endpoint that was auto-disabled due to\n"
"    consecutive failures."
msgstr ""
"Atur ulang jumlah kegagalan untuk titik akhir webhook.\n"
"\n"
"Ini mengaktifkan kembali titik akhir yang secara otomatis dinonaktifkan "
"karena\n"
"kegagalan berurutan."

msgid "List webhook deliveries"
msgstr "Daftar pengiriman webhook"

msgid "Get webhook delivery logs with optional filtering."
msgstr "Dapatkan log pengiriman webhook dengan penyaringan opsional."

msgid "Filter by endpoint UUID"
msgstr "Saring berdasarkan UUID akhir"

msgid "Filter by event type (e.g., order.created)"
msgstr "Saring berdasarkan jenis acara (misalnya, order.created)"

msgid "Filter by delivery status"
msgstr "Saring berdasarkan status pengiriman"

msgid "Number of results to return (default 50, max 200)"
msgstr "Jumlah hasil yang dikembalikan (default 50, maks 200)"

msgid "Get webhook delivery"
msgstr "Dapatkan pengiriman webhook"

msgid "Get details of a specific webhook delivery including the full payload."
msgstr "Dapatkan detail pengiriman webhook tertentu termasuk payload lengkap."

msgid "Delivery not found"
msgstr "Pengiriman tidak ditemukan"

msgid "Retry webhook delivery"
msgstr "Coba kembali pengiriman webhook"

msgid ""
"Manually retry a failed webhook delivery.\n"
"\n"
"    This queues the delivery for immediate retry, regardless of\n"
"    the scheduled retry time."
msgstr ""
"Coba kirim ulang pengiriman webhook yang gagal secara manual.\n"
"\n"
"Ini akan memasukkan pengiriman ke dalam antrian untuk dicoba kembali segera, "
"tanpa memandang\n"
"waktu ulang coba yang telah dijadwalkan."

msgid "Cannot retry this delivery"
msgstr "Tidak dapat mencoba kembali pengiriman ini"

msgid "List webhook event types"
msgstr "Daftar jenis acara webhook"

msgid ""
"Get all available webhook event types.\n"
"\n"
"    Returns a list of events that can be subscribed to when\n"
"    creating a webhook endpoint."
msgstr ""
"Dapatkan semua jenis acara webhook yang tersedia.\n"
"\n"
"Mengembalikan daftar acara yang dapat berlangganan saat\n"
"membuat titik akhir webhook."

msgid "Get webhook documentation"
msgstr "Dapatkan dokumentasi webhook"

msgid ""
"Get comprehensive documentation for webhook integration.\n"
"\n"
"    Returns all available event types, payload schemas, signature "
"verification\n"
"    instructions, and code examples for integrating with the webhook "
"system.\n"
"\n"
"    This endpoint is publicly accessible to allow external developers to\n"
"    understand webhook payloads without authentication."
msgstr ""
"Dapatkan dokumentasi komprehensif untuk integrasi webhook.\n"
"\n"
"Mengembalikan semua jenis acara yang tersedia, skema payload, instruksi "
"verifikasi tanda tangan,\n"
"dan contoh kode untuk mengintegrasikan dengan sistem webhook.\n"
"\n"
"Endpoint ini dapat diakses secara umum untuk memungkinkan pengembang "
"eksternal\n"
"memahami payload webhook tanpa otentikasi."

msgid "Get webhook endpoint stats"
msgstr "Dapatkan statistik akhir webhook"

msgid "Get delivery statistics for a webhook endpoint."
msgstr "Dapatkan statistik pengiriman untuk akhir titik webhook."

