msgid ""
"Spwig webhooks allow you to receive real-time HTTP notifications when events "
"occur in your store. This enables you to build integrations, sync data with "
"external systems, and automate workflows."
msgstr ""
"Webhook Spwig memungkinkan Anda menerima notifikasi HTTP real-time ketika "
"acara terjadi di toko Anda. Ini memungkinkan Anda membangun integrasi, "
"menyinkronkan data dengan sistem eksternal, dan mengotomatisasi alur kerja."

msgid "Real-time"
msgstr "Waktu nyata"

msgid "Receive instant notifications when events occur"
msgstr "Terima notifikasi instan ketika acara terjadi"

msgid "Secure"
msgstr "Aman"

msgid "HMAC-SHA256 signed payloads for verification"
msgstr "Payloads yang ditandatangani dengan HMAC-SHA256 untuk verifikasi"

msgid "Reliable"
msgstr "Andal"

msgid "Automatic retries with exponential backoff"
msgstr "Pengulangan otomatis dengan backoff eksponensial"

msgid "Getting Started"
msgstr "Memulai"

msgid "Create an endpoint"
msgstr "Buat endpoint"

msgid ""
"Configure a webhook endpoint in your admin dashboard with the URL where you "
"want to receive webhooks."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurasikan endpoint webhook di dashboard admin Anda dengan URL tempat "
"Anda ingin menerima webhook."

msgid "Subscribe to events"
msgstr "Langgani acara"

msgid "Choose which events you want to receive notifications for."
msgstr "Pilih acara yang ingin Anda terima notifikasi untuk."

msgid "Implement verification"
msgstr "Implementasikan verifikasi"

msgid "Use HMAC-SHA256 to verify that webhooks are authentic."
msgstr "Gunakan HMAC-SHA256 untuk memverifikasi bahwa webhook adalah asli."

msgid "Handle payloads"
msgstr "Proses payloads"

msgid "Process the JSON payloads in your application."
msgstr "Proses payload JSON dalam aplikasi Anda."

msgid "Headers"
msgstr "Headers"

msgid "Every webhook request includes the following headers:"
msgstr "Setiap permintaan webhook mencakup header berikut:"

msgid "Header"
msgstr "Header"

msgid "Description"
msgstr "Deskripsi"

msgid "Example"
msgstr "Contoh"

msgid "HMAC-SHA256 signature for verification"
msgstr "Tanda tangan HMAC-SHA256 untuk verifikasi"

msgid "The event type"
msgstr "Jenis acara"

msgid "Unique delivery identifier (UUID)"
msgstr "Identifikasi pengiriman unik (UUID)"

msgid "Unix timestamp when sent"
msgstr "Tanda waktu Unix saat dikirim"

msgid "Content type"
msgstr "Jenis konten"

msgid "Webhook user agent"
msgstr "User agent webhook"

msgid "Available Events"
msgstr "Acara Tersedia"

msgid "Subscribe to any of the following events. You can use"
msgstr "Langgani salah satu dari acara berikut. Anda dapat menggunakan"

msgid "to subscribe to all events."
msgstr "untuk berlangganan semua acara."

msgid "Payload Structure"
msgstr "Struktur Payload"

msgid "All webhook payloads follow this structure:"
msgstr "Semua payload webhook mengikuti struktur ini:"

msgid "Example: Order Created"
msgstr "Contoh: Pesanan Dibuat"

msgid "Payload Schemas by Category"
msgstr "Skema Payload Berdasarkan Kategori"

msgid "Field"
msgstr "Field"

msgid "Type"
msgstr "Tipe"

msgid "Important:"
msgstr "Penting:"

msgid ""
"Always verify webhook signatures before processing payloads to ensure they "
"are authentic and haven't been tampered with."
msgstr ""
"Selalu verifikasi tanda tangan webhook sebelum memproses payload untuk "
"memastikan bahwa mereka asli dan tidak dimanipulasi."

msgid "Verification Steps"
msgstr "Langkah Verifikasi"

msgid "Extract the timestamp and signature"
msgstr "Ekstrak tanda waktu dan tanda tangan"

msgid "Parse the"
msgstr "Parse"

msgid "header:"
msgstr "header:"

msgid "Compute the expected signature"
msgstr "Hitung tanda tangan yang diharapkan"

msgid "Create the signature payload and compute HMAC-SHA256:"
msgstr "Buat payload tanda tangan dan hitung HMAC-SHA256:"

msgid "Compare signatures"
msgstr "Bandingkan tanda tangan"

msgid "Use constant-time comparison to prevent timing attacks."
msgstr "Gunakan perbandingan waktu konstan untuk mencegah serangan waktu."

msgid "Verify timestamp"
msgstr "Verifikasi tanda waktu"

msgid "Ensure the timestamp is within 5 minutes to prevent replay attacks."
msgstr "Pastikan timestamp berada dalam 5 menit untuk mencegah serangan ulang."

msgid ""
"Failed webhook deliveries are automatically retried with exponential backoff:"
msgstr ""
"Pengiriman webhook yang gagal secara otomatis dicoba kembali dengan backoff "
"eksponensial:"

msgid "Attempt"
msgstr "Coba"

msgid "Delay"
msgstr "Tunda"

msgid "Immediate"
msgstr "Segera"

msgid "1 minute"
msgstr "1 menit"

msgid "2 minutes"
msgstr "2 menit"

msgid "4 minutes"
msgstr "4 menit"

msgid "8 minutes"
msgstr "8 menit"

msgid "Important Notes"
msgstr "Catatan Penting"

msgid "Webhooks are considered successful if they return a 2xx status code."
msgstr "Webhook dianggap berhasil jika mereka mengembalikan kode status 2xx."

msgid "Your endpoint should respond within 30 seconds."
msgstr "Endpoint Anda harus merespons dalam 30 detik."

msgid "After 5 failed attempts, the delivery is marked as failed."
msgstr "Setelah 5 percobaan gagal, pengiriman ditandai sebagai gagal."

msgid "After 10 consecutive failures, the endpoint is automatically disabled."
msgstr ""
"Setelah 10 kegagalan berurutan, endpoint secara otomatis dinonaktifkan."

msgid "API Reference"
msgstr "Referensi API"

msgid ""
"For programmatic access to this documentation, use the Webhook Documentation "
"API:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk akses program ke dokumentasi ini, gunakan Webhook Documentation API:"

msgid ""
"This returns the complete documentation as JSON, including all event types "
"and payload schemas."
