msgstr "Sistem Webhook"

msgid ""
"Webhooks allow external systems to receive real-time HTTP notifications when "
"events occur in your store, such as new orders, payments, or shipments."
msgstr ""
"Webhook memungkinkan sistem eksternal menerima notifikasi HTTP real-time "
"ketika acara terjadi di toko Anda, seperti pesanan baru, pembayaran, atau "
"pengiriman."

msgid "Features:"
