msgstr "Buat Titik Akhir"

msgid "Set up a new webhook endpoint to receive real-time notifications"
msgstr "Buat endpoint webhook baru untuk menerima notifikasi real-time"

msgid "Endpoint Details"
msgstr "Detail Titik Akhir"

msgid "Select Events"
msgstr "Pilih Acara"

msgid "Review"
msgstr "Ulasan"

msgid "Enter the basic information for your webhook endpoint."
msgstr "Masukkan informasi dasar untuk endpoint webhook Anda."

msgid "Tip:"
msgstr "Tips:"

msgid ""
"Use a descriptive name like 'Order Sync - ERP' or 'Inventory Updates'. The "
"URL should point to your webhook receiver endpoint."
msgstr ""
"Gunakan nama deskriptif seperti 'Order Sync - ERP' atau 'Inventory Updates'. "
"URL harus mengarah ke endpoint penerima webhook Anda."

msgid "Endpoint Name"
msgstr "Nama Titik Akhir"

msgid "e.g., Order Notifications, Inventory Sync"
msgstr "Contoh: Pemberitahuan Pesanan, Sinkronisasi Inventaris"

msgid "A friendly name to identify this endpoint"
msgstr "Nama ramah untuk mengidentifikasi endpoint ini"

msgid "Webhook URL"
msgstr "URL Webhook"

msgid ""
"Must be HTTPS in production. This is where webhook payloads will be sent."
msgstr ""
"Harus HTTPS dalam produksi. Ini adalah tempat payload webhook akan "
"dikirimkan."

msgid "Optional: Describe what this endpoint is used for..."
msgstr "Opsional: Deskripsikan apa yang digunakan endpoint ini untuk..."

msgid ""
"Choose which events this endpoint should receive. You can select individual "
"events or subscribe to all events."
msgstr ""
"Pilih acara yang harus diterima oleh endpoint ini. Anda dapat memilih acara "
"individual atau berlangganan semua acara."

msgid "Subscribe to all events"
msgstr "Langgani semua acara"

msgid "Includes all current and future event types"
msgstr "Termasuk semua jenis acara saat ini dan masa depan"

msgid "events selected"
msgstr "acara terpilih"

msgid "Select all"
msgstr "Pilih semua"

msgid "Configure retry behavior and timeout settings for this endpoint."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurasikan perilaku pengulangan dan pengaturan timeout untuk endpoint "
"ini."

msgid "Retry Settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan Ulang Coba"

msgid "Maximum Retries"
msgstr "Maksimum Percobaan"

msgid ""
"Number of times to retry if delivery fails (0-10). Uses exponential backoff."
msgstr ""
"Jumlah kali untuk mencoba kembali jika pengiriman gagal (0-10). Menggunakan "
"backoff eksponensial."

msgid "Retry Schedule:"
msgstr "Jadwal Ulang Coba:"

msgid ""
"Failed deliveries are retried with exponential backoff: 1 minute, 2 minutes, "
"4 minutes, 8 minutes, etc."
msgstr ""
"Pengiriman yang gagal dicoba kembali dengan backoff eksponensial: 1 menit, 2 "
"menit, 4 menit, 8 menit, dst."

msgid "Timeout Settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan Timeout"

msgid "Request Timeout (seconds)"
msgstr "Timeout Permintaan (detik)"

msgid "How long to wait for a response before timing out (5-60 seconds)."
msgstr "Berapa lama menunggu respons sebelum timeout (5-60 detik)."

msgid "Inactive endpoints will not receive webhook deliveries."
msgstr "Endpoint yang tidak aktif tidak akan menerima pengiriman webhook."

msgid "Auto-Disable Protection:"
msgstr "Perlindungan Auto-Nonaktif:"

msgid ""
"Endpoints are automatically disabled after 10 consecutive failures to "
"protect your system. You can re-enable them from the endpoint list."
msgstr ""
"Endpoint akan dinonaktifkan secara otomatis setelah 10 kegagalan berturut-"
"turut untuk melindungi sistem Anda. Anda dapat mengaktifkannya kembali dari "
"daftar endpoint."

msgid "Review & Create"
msgstr "Periksa & Buat"

msgid "Review your webhook endpoint configuration before creating it."
msgstr "Periksa konfigurasi endpoint webhook Anda sebelum membuatnya."

